  <summary>4/23/2002--Introduced.
Defense Recurring Reports Elimination Act of 2002 - Amends Federal armed forces provisions, certain prior defense authorization and appropriations Acts, the Defense Acquisition Improvement Act of 1986, the Ballistic Missile Defense Act of 1995, and the Military Construction Appropriations Act, 2001 to repeal various reporting requirements imposed on the Department of Defense.</summary>
